500,000 euros, which is a

00:03:59.270 --> 00:04:01.650
cash output and we have a series

00:04:01.650 --> 00:04:03.310
of positive cash flows

00:04:03.310 --> 00:04:04.950
entries in the next four years,

00:04:04.950 --> 00:04:07.150
