Let’s look at this example, let’s

00:05:04.510 --> 00:05:06.610
see it with a little more of detail

00:05:06.610 --> 00:05:07.830
at a numerical level.

00:05:07.890 --> 00:05:11.610
We have cash flows that are the investment

00:05:11.610 --> 00:05:13.730
of 500,000 and then the charges

00:05:13.730 --> 00:05:15.730
we receive in the next

00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:17.110
